    <section id="id1607009">
      <title>[LO 1.14]</title>
      <para id="id2764221">Make a sketch of the side elevation of your rocket. Sketch the fins as well and draw as accurately as possible.</para>
      <list id="id1925258" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>The centre of pressure is determined by drawing a line that spreads the surface of the rocket equally on both sides of the line.</item>
        <item>Indicate the centre of pressure in the sketch by drawing a line through it.</item>
        <item>Indicate the centre of pressure on the rocket by drawing a line right around the body with a marking-pen. Indicate the symbol for the centre of pressure.  </item>
      </list>
